videos.description: Baylor's Manu Lecomte takes it through the paint and finishes with a layup against Texas.
videos.headline: Lecomte muscles through the paint for lay-in

videos.description: Eric Davis Jr. hits a three-pointer from deep to put the Longhorns ahead.
videos.headline: Texas' Davis drains it from deep

videos.description: Texas' Jericho Sims gets the pass and finishes with a dunk against Baylor.
videos.headline: Sims slams one home

videos.description: Texas' Matt Coleman tosses it up on a fast break for Mohamed Bamba who jams it.
videos.headline: Coleman finds Bamba for alley-oop

videos.description: Terry Maston grabs the offensive rebound and powers through for up-and-under layup.
videos.headline: Maston goes up and under

videos.description: Jake Lindsey tops off Baylor's 7-0 run with game-tying lay in from Manu Lecomte.
videos.headline: Lindsey ties game on breakaway layup

videos.description: Kerwin Roach creates a huge momentum swing with the steal and he finishes with a huge one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Roach's steal and slam

videos.description: Manu Lecomte drives for the layup, but his scoring attempt is slapped away by Texas' Manu Bamba.
videos.headline: Bamba sends Lecomte's layup into the stands

videos.description: Eric Davis Jr. drives and lobs it up for a Mohamed Bamba dunk.
videos.headline: Bamba's thrown down two-handed jam for Texas

videos.description: Texas' Eric Davis Jr. misses his jumper but Mohamed Bamba is there to tip in the rebound.
videos.headline: Bamba cleans up around the rim
